Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.93,0:00:06.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼叫普特利麥奧斯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.12,0:00:08.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是GN ARMS  拉塞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.53,0:00:13.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在開始強襲用運輸器的對接程序
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.78,0:00:14.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.81,0:00:16.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與運輸器的相對速度OK
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.89,0:00:19.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軌道  激光  鎖定
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.03,0:00:34.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN ARMS與強襲用運輸器對接完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.22,0:00:37.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了  相當不錯的戰果啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.38,0:00:40.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔  洛克恩的情況如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.36,0:00:44.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬幸的是身體上的傷並不嚴重
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.88,0:00:46.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是右眼就受創了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.26,0:00:49.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在在集中治療室
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.44,0:00:53.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫雷諾醫生  傷口要多久才能恢復？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.09,0:00:56.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最少也要三週
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.02,0:01:00.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想必你也知道  一旦進了治療艙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.22,0:01:01.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒治好之前不能出來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.39,0:01:03.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,治療就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.74,0:01:08.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此期間我們先回船塢把Gundam的整備…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.58,0:01:11.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  別隨便下決定啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.92,0:01:12.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克恩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.20,0:01:15.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人不知道什麼時候會來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.82,0:01:17.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用治療了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.43,0:01:20.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  以你的傷根本不能進行精確射擊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.00,0:01:23.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別小瞧我和哈羅的組合哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.19,0:01:25.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然  當然
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.05,0:01:30.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  如果我躺著的話有個傢伙會很在意
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.60,0:01:34.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再怎麼要強  那傢伙也很脆弱…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.19,0:01:40.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因為我過於依賴吠陀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.23,0:01:43.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而讓他負了傷
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.61,0:01:46.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.96,0:03:26.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次  我們聯合國軍將開發能與Gundam對抗的新型MS
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.19,0:03:27.10,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(500,0)}聯合  美國  伊利諾伊基地
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.38,0:03:30.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將此新型機編為特別部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.53,0:03:32.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始對Gundam進行掃蕩作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.66,0:03:36.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作戰名為Fallen Angels
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.81,0:03:38.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於公開了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.74,0:03:41.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得簡直就像是自己造出來的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.40,0:03:43.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Flag的狀況呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.45,0:03:48.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如你所見  正在全力突擊作業
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.43,0:03:51.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你再等等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.80,0:03:53.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最怕等待
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.25,0:03:55.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.95,0:04:01.36,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}人革聯  俄羅斯南部  軍事基地
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.52,0:04:11.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中校  所有GN Drive的壓縮空間在臨界值上穩定了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.83,0:04:12.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,點火
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.27,0:04:13.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.47,0:04:29.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN-X  啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.80,0:04:37.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在重新開始對Gundam進行掃蕩作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.50,0:04:40.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN-X部隊  全體出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.92,0:04:50.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次不會讓你們逃掉了…Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.06,0:05:01.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam的整備狀況如何了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.48,0:05:04.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Virtue的損傷還有辦法處理
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.27,0:05:06.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dynames呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.64,0:05:09.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊  駕駛艙的損壞嚴重
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.15,0:05:11.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毀壞成這樣  無從修起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.41,0:05:15.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得回船塢換一些單元
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.91,0:05:19.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能活動的Gundam只有三台…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.53,0:05:23.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼Fallen Angels啊  開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.92,0:05:26.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我們是墜落的天使呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.76,0:05:29.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說來  菲露特呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.83,0:05:31.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多是那種年紀了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.30,0:05:33.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.58,0:05:35.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  遲鈍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.65,0:05:36.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.82,0:05:41.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克恩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.58,0:05:48.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想一直這樣多久
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.01,0:05:51.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不像你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.74,0:05:55.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像平時那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.48,0:05:57.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.88,0:05:58.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.29,0:06:02.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我失去了作為Meister的資格了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.40,0:06:07.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不能和吠陀直接連接的話  我已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.44,0:06:11.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和吠陀的直接連接…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.75,0:06:14.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇小姐  Virtue的系統變更出錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.71,0:06:21.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新系統傳送時出錯是因為連接中的特瑞亞自身引起了障礙…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.29,0:06:24.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  這種事對於人類…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.12,0:06:28.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不適合當Meister
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.31,0:06:31.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不適合嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.85,0:06:33.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是沒什麼關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.65,0:06:34.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.84,0:06:37.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過是不能連接而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.89,0:06:40.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就當變得跟我們一樣就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.40,0:06:43.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吠陀被什麼人掌握了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.39,0:06:46.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有吠陀的話  這個計劃…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.39,0:06:47.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能行的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.24,0:06:53.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是為了根除戰爭才坐上Gundam戰鬥的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.83,0:06:56.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  實現計劃的可能性已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.87,0:06:59.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別管那麼多  做就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.10,0:07:02.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你身邊不是就有個做示範的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.67,0:07:07.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只會按自己的想法亂搞一氣的笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.61,0:07:12.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己的想法…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.03,0:07:15.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了  我回房間休息去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.90,0:07:16.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克恩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.04,0:07:17.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.68,0:07:19.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.57,0:07:23.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇小姐也說過的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.71,0:07:27.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失敗是很正常的啊  因為是人類嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.25,0:07:33.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真溫柔啊  不管是對誰…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.74,0:07:37.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  想吃肉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.26,0:07:40.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罐頭我都吃膩了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.18,0:07:42.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想吃甜食
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.83,0:07:45.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底要逃到什麼時候啊  大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.11,0:07:48.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粒子也剩得不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.67,0:07:52.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望將我們和機體一起返回宇宙的事能準備就緒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.43,0:07:56.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樂意效勞…本想這麼說的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.72,0:07:58.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微晚了一些
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.73,0:07:59.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.70,0:08:02.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯合國軍的部隊已經朝你們那裡出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.23,0:08:04.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.48,0:08:05.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早做準備
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.68,0:08:07.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邁克爾  妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.24,0:08:10.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啟動Throne  快點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.18,0:08:14.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中校  發現Gundam了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.72,0:08:16.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地點E8590
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.20,0:08:19.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全機  迎擊隊形
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.60,0:08:20.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.43,0:08:29.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邁克爾  妮娜  Drive的粒子發生率在下降
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.43,0:08:30.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要浪費
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.29,0:08:31.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.07,0:08:32.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.03,0:08:35.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還剩30%嗎  但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.40,0:08:37.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,散開
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.19,0:08:45.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然對不起大哥  但我可不會節省的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.33,0:08:47.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧  Fang
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.96,0:08:52.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,密集隊形
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.76,0:09:02.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有你們的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.60,0:09:06.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該死
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.31,0:09:08.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我下去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.49,0:09:09.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來一次攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.86,0:09:19.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam正在鄰國的領空交戰？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.57,0:09:22.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯合國的掃蕩作戰開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.37,0:09:24.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種機體…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.33,0:09:27.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…不是刹那的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.87,0:09:37.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快被幹掉啊  Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.27,0:09:42.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該死
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.99,0:09:43.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.96,0:09:45.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別以為人多就…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.47,0:09:49.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼笨拙的攻擊怎麼可能打中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.91,0:09:56.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超兵的實力  覺悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.67,0:09:58.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.07,0:10:01.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤退了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.14,0:10:03.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了…瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.13,0:10:06.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡  我們還是Gundam啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.87,0:10:11.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別想逃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.60,0:10:14.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用追了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.91,0:10:15.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.05,0:10:17.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們的藏身所已經被破壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.33,0:10:20.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Drive的活動界限遲早會到的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.06,0:10:28.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Level 6  Clear
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.09,0:10:30.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進入最終作業
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.88,0:10:35.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Trinity的極限快到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.33,0:10:39.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  最後的餘興節目  讓我期待一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.38,0:10:54.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯合國軍終於對Trinity開始攻擊了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.28,0:10:58.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了擊敗Gundam  世界在統一
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.70,0:11:03.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然我們是為了被毀滅而存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.85,0:11:07.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是伊奧利亞·修亨伯格的計劃…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.57,0:11:08.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.03,0:11:10.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會有Gundam？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.58,0:11:15.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根除戰爭的機體應該是Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.23,0:11:20.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  Trinity把戰火擴大  聯合國軍也…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.25,0:11:24.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是Gundam要做的事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.79,0:11:26.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.18,0:11:31.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那  聯合國軍對Trinity的攻擊也是紛爭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.30,0:11:34.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有必要進行武力介入
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.54,0:11:36.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.69,0:11:37.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太亂來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.77,0:11:39.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們已經很疲勞了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.54,0:11:41.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軌道電梯也不能使用
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.83,0:11:46.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前受到敵人攻擊也是因為Exia和Dynames被敵人跟蹤
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.39,0:11:49.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Celestial Being不允許沉默
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.78,0:11:50.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧  刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.46,0:11:52.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.75,0:11:55.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能沒辦法再回宇宙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.88,0:11:58.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是一個人也要去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.03,0:12:03.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想確認Gundam到底是為什麼存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.65,0:12:05.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.60,0:12:08.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受傷的就老實待著
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.24,0:12:09.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.34,0:12:11.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉塞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.27,0:12:14.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強襲用運輸器有衝出大氣層的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.53,0:12:17.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順便也能做GN Arms的性能試驗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.27,0:12:19.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在分散戰力的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.30,0:12:26.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任務計劃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.06,0:12:31.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不確定因素太多了  可能沒什麼用處
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.16,0:12:34.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要回來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.61,0:12:36.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.21,0:12:41.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exia  強襲用運輸器搭載完成
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.41,0:12:45.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN Drive與運輸器的對接確認
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.30,0:12:48.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發射準備  全部正常
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.60,0:12:52.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那  能得到答案就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.32,0:12:53.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.25,0:12:55.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任務開始
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.27,0:12:56.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.19,0:12:59.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強襲用運輸器  拉塞  出發
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.12,0:13:12.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想去的話  你也可以去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.03,0:13:14.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擔心刹那吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.32,0:13:16.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很笨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.33,0:13:19.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.82,0:13:26.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.28,0:13:27.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.31,0:13:32.54,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(500,500)}AEU  高軌道平台
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.60,0:13:32.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突入大氣層的機體？所屬呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.68,0:13:37.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不明  但是突入前觀測組發現了GN粒子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.72,0:13:39.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了  馬上就去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.34,0:13:44.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Celestial Being是想去幫留在地上的同伴嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.49,0:13:52.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我的Drei被…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.24,0:13:54.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦啊  大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.51,0:13:58.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經拜託王留美做上宇宙的準備了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.79,0:14:00.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能信任她嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.09,0:14:02.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.38,0:14:07.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AEU的Enact
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.28,0:14:09.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光通訊？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.76,0:14:12.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說沒有攻擊意圖？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.08,0:14:14.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜  在Throne待機
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.13,0:14:15.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.25,0:14:30.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲  到處與世界為敵的就是你們嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.16,0:14:31.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什麼人？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.19,0:14:34.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿里·阿爾·沙謝斯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.47,0:14:37.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如你所見  是個傭兵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.69,0:14:40.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贊助商要我來給你們幫點什麼忙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.30,0:14:44.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,援軍不是就一架嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.98,0:14:47.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰讓你來的？  拉古那嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.64,0:14:51.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉古那？  啊  你是說拉古那·哈貝嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.09,0:14:53.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他已經死了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.71,0:14:54.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.00,0:14:57.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我殺的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.05,0:14:58.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邁克爾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.76,0:15:01.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邁克哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.74,0:15:02.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.12,0:15:03.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.13,0:15:09.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約翰哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.77,0:15:11.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快…快逃  妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.31,0:15:13.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.33,0:15:14.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.57,0:15:15.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.12,0:15:18.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是美麗的兄妹之愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.93,0:15:21.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點坐上機體如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.96,0:15:23.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣根本打不起來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.58,0:15:27.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.83,0:15:33.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約翰哥  邁克哥被…  邁克哥被！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.78,0:15:34.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會替他報仇的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.46,0:15:35.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.63,0:15:37.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.40,0:15:42.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會？Zwei沒有邁克爾的生物識別的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.71,0:15:46.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,資料被改寫了嗎！？用了吠陀！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.96,0:15:49.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不習慣的話不方便操作
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.48,0:15:52.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但只要知道了武裝  之後總有辦法的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.02,0:15:54.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？  為什麼對我們
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.99,0:15:56.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是活祭哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.39,0:15:57.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.59,0:15:58.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深表同情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.75,0:15:59.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可憐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.06,0:16:02.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是Gundam Meister
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.41,0:16:08.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了改變這個世界！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.64,0:16:10.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.32,0:16:13.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經夠多了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.79,0:16:15.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約翰哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.92,0:16:16.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安心的去吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.35,0:16:26.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…我們是為成為Meister而生的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.76,0:16:29.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為此  而活著…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.67,0:16:44.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN粒子真是漂亮的東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.40,0:16:46.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧  小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.46,0:16:53.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈哈哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.43,0:16:56.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.12,0:17:02.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別來搗亂啊  克魯吉斯的小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.31,0:17:05.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿里·阿爾·沙謝斯！？  為什麼！？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.99,0:17:07.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你會坐上Gundam！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.63,0:17:11.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Level 7  Clear
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.59,0:17:13.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全掌握吠陀了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.23,0:17:16.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  終於…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.33,0:17:33.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然在這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.14,0:17:35.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊奧利亞·修亨伯格
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.47,0:17:38.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了看到世界的變革
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.10,0:17:42.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有蘇醒的保證就進入冷凍休眠…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.65,0:17:49.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  很可惜你無法看到世界的變革
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.24,0:17:52.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所追求的統一的世界也好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.08,0:17:56.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為其抑制力的Celestial Being也好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.57,0:17:58.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都將由我來繼承
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.25,0:18:00.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.73,0:18:05.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改變世界的是我——亞歷桑德羅·柯納
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.52,0:18:22.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.00,0:18:24.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,李本茲  這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.20,0:18:34.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡出現懷有惡意的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.79,0:18:39.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說很可惜  世界並沒有成為我所追求的那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.43,0:18:41.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊…伊奧利亞·修亨伯格
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.36,0:18:43.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,系統陷阱…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.24,0:18:46.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類現在還很愚蠢好戰
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.65,0:18:51.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在走向讓世界毀滅的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.58,0:18:53.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來啊來啊！怎麼啦？Gundam！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.81,0:18:56.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這樣的人居然坐上Gundam…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.88,0:18:59.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需要你小子的許可
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.51,0:19:04.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  我還是相信人類…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.05,0:19:11.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想將力量託付給他們
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.12,0:19:13.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.90,0:19:18.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好準確的射擊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.85,0:19:20.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了  Gundam這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.27,0:19:22.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.78,0:19:26.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.14,0:19:29.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.38,0:19:32.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙還真是了不得的兵器啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.31,0:19:33.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,值得進行戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.53,0:19:36.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的Gundam就是為此而存在的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.51,0:19:38.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.50,0:19:41.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.81,0:19:42.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.42,0:19:45.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.89,0:19:48.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一來就了結你！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.95,0:19:52.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不得不改變了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.62,0:20:03.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？在哪裡！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.79,0:20:08.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？那種動作是？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.39,0:20:10.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.02,0:20:13.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打不中！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.02,0:20:14.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我的背後！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.51,0:20:23.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.83,0:20:26.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exia…  變紅了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.58,0:20:37.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這台Gundam…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.38,0:20:40.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擁有GN Drive的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.23,0:20:42.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.70,0:20:44.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊奧利亞·修亨伯格
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.68,0:20:46.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是否是我的意識的繼承者我並不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.13,0:20:50.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  我想把我最後的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.09,0:20:55.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN Drive的全部能力託付給你們
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.72,0:20:59.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祈禱你們為了獲得真正的和平
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.32,0:21:03.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了根除戰爭而繼續奮戰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.11,0:21:07.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是為了Celestial Being
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.08,0:21:09.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是以你們的意識…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.12,0:21:11.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同Gundam一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.99,0:21:15.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.71,0:21:19.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不知道是什麼把戲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.24,0:21:25.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老子我會…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.32,0:21:35.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了…那到底是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.08,0:21:47.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TRANS-AM…系統…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.37,0:21:49.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.54,0:21:51.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TRANS-AM
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.52,0:22:17.89,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}同じ笑顔してた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.16,0:22:24.72,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}そんな僕らも幾年も重ねすぎて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.13,0:22:28.41,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}すれ違う景色を
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.66,0:22:33.62,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}受け入れられずにもがいてる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.84,0:22:40.84,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}無駄なプライド捨て去り
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.16,0:22:46.53,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}この世界に優しさを
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.67,0:22:47.72,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}I Gotta Say
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.90,0:22:53.10,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}勇気を見せつけても　強がっても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.25,0:22:57.81,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}一人では生きられない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.36,0:23:02.14,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}あの日の約束なら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.45,0:23:07.24,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}心の深くに残っているよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.47,0:23:12.58,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}As life goes on...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.91,0:23:18.02,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}忘れちゃいけないからYeah
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.26,0:23:23.24,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}Don't let it go...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.58,0:23:30.57,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}この広い大地の仲間たちのこと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.52,0:22:17.89,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}曾有著相同的笑臉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.16,0:22:24.72,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}就是那樣的我們也已過了多年
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.13,0:22:28.41,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}那交錯的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.66,0:22:33.62,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}無法接受並急躁著
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.84,0:22:40.84,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}捨棄了無用的自尊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.16,0:22:46.53,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}給予這世界以溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.67,0:22:47.72,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}我要說
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.90,0:22:53.10,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}即便顯示出勇氣　即便逞強
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.25,0:22:57.81,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}一個人亦是無法生存的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.36,0:23:02.14,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}若是那天的約定
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.45,0:23:07.24,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}依然存留在心靈深處的話
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.47,0:23:12.58,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}如同生命的延續...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.91,0:23:18.02,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}由於不可忘記　Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.26,0:23:23.24,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}所以不要離去...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.58,0:23:30.57,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}還要留在這廣闊大地同伴們的身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.98,0:23:36.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界和人的意識改變了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.42,0:23:40.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  反對的意識在呐喊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.10,0:23:43.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集  「把世界停住」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.88,0:23:47.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不絕的慟哭駐留在漆黑的天空


